				  MUI group. Filetype search work works incrementally.
 40.20	20080831	jl      - Bugfix: search filetypes list with "Find next" didn't work.
 40.18	20080518	jl	- Bugfix: Adding new methods for filetypes' recognition was broken.
			jl	- Improvement: extended DefIcons functionality to cover classification
				  of WBDISK objects, i.e. USB disks, DVDs or SMB network volumes are now
                                  recognized automatically.
