-------------------xtwindows.plugin-----------------------------------------

 40.6  	20050325	JL	- Adapted XTWindows.plugin for PPC/MorphOS.
 40.5	20040102	JL	- Adapted to changed OpenDrawerByName() function, now 
				  uses iconobject.library instead of icon.library.

-------------------- sorted_cleanup.plugin ---------------------------------

 39.4	20050320	JL	- sorted_cleanup.s: New attempt to fix refresh
				  problems with sort_cleanup.

